// Screen heading HUD configuration
// Controls the layout of the large heading text shown at the top of each screen.
// Text content and color are screen-specific; only layout parameters live here.
//
// Hot-reload enabled: Edit this file while the game is running to see changes instantly!
//
// Parameters:
// - font_size:     Font size of the heading text in points
// - margin_bottom: Bottom margin below the heading in pixels (spacing before the next element)

ScreenHeadingHudConfig(
    font_size:     72.0,
    margin_bottom: 80.0,
)
